'''[[金馬獎|金馬獎]]最佳動畫短片'''，原為「最佳創作短片」，為推動並鼓勵華語動畫創作，特將其分為「最佳劇情短片」及「最佳動畫短片」兩獎項頒發。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.goldenhorse.org.tw/awards/about/milestones/|title=台北金馬影展 Taipei Golden Horse Film Festival|accessdate=2018-09-10|work=www.goldenhorse.org.tw|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2015-11-03|archive-url=https://archive.is/20151103010104/http://yule.sohu.com/20090413/n263344639.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>是由[[財團法人中華民國電影事業發展基金會|財團法人中華民國電影事業發展基金會]]的[[臺北金馬影展執行委員會|臺北金馬影展執行委員會]]在[[臺灣|臺灣]]舉辦的電影獎項，自2016年起頒發，獎勵在華語電影中的電影獎項<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160324/823790/ |title = 金馬獎增設動畫短片獎　想搶獎的準備報名 |author = 張哲鳴 |date = 2016-03-24 |publisher = 蘋果日報 |language = zh-hant |accessdate = 2016-04-05 |archive-date = 2016-03-30 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160330014722/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160324/823790/ |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.cna.com.tw/news/amov/201603240380-1.aspx |title = 金馬53增設動畫短片 3導拍形象廣告 |author = 王靖怡 |date = 2016-03-24 |publisher = 中央社 |language = zh-hant |accessdate = 2016-04-05 |archive-date = 2016-03-27 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160327222740/http://www.cna.com.tw/news/amov/201603240380-1.aspx |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://movies.ettoday.net/news/669061 |title = 趙德胤、陳哲藝、畢贛挺金馬53　形象廣告將曝光 |author = 林映妤 |date = 2016-03-24 |publisher = 東森新聞 |language = zh-hant |accessdate = 2016-04-05 |archive-date = 2016-04-06 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160406111923/http://movies.ettoday.net/news/669061 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20160325000013-260404 |title = 趙德胤、陳哲藝、畢贛 替「金馬53」拍廣告 |author = 潘鈺楨 |date = 2016-03-25 |publisher = 東森新聞 |language = zh-hant |accessdate = 2016-04-05 |archive-date = 2016-04-08 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160408043202/http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20160325000013-260404 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

